title: Borderlands GOTY Edition RF XBOX360-SREYALP4

Borderlands 1 Game Of The Year Edition.
Category: Xbox360 ISO

Developed by Gearbox Software, Borderlands combines first-person action with player customization and vehicular combat to create an unprecedented gaming experience. 
Borderlands is an extraordinary cooperative experience, allowing for multiple players to share the experience online gaming at the same time, may join or leave each other's games at anytime, or choose to play in the full single-player mode. Borderlands features animations as realistic characters, an impressive real-time physics and a variety of customizable vehicles.
